      "seed": 14, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "Job 2: eval  (needs: validate)\n\n1. checkout skill-testing-playground @ main  (read-only)\n2. detect changed skill  (git diff HEAD^1)\n3. pip install -e .\n4. start mock MCP server &\n5. python -m eval.ab_compare \\\n     --skill-path <changed-skill> --trials 5\n6. post PR comment  (verdict + Langfuse trace links)\n\nSecrets: EVAL_PLATFORM_TOKEN  OPENROUTER_API_KEY\n         LANGFUSE_PUBLIC_KEY  LANGFUSE_SECRET_KEY  LANGFUSE_HOST", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 13, "containerId": null, "originalText": "", "lineHeight": 1.4
