      "roundness": null, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "boundElements": [],
      "seed": 20, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "A/B Harness  (eval/ab_compare.py)\n\n--skill-path <any repo dir>\n--trials N\n\nTask loading:\n1. Exact match: task.toml skill=\"name\"\n2. Semantic fallback: SkillRouter\n   (cosine sim, threshold 0.35)\n\nPer task × N trials:\n  condition A: no_skill baseline\n  condition B: with_skill injected\n  best-of-N score per condition", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 13, "containerId": null, "originalText": "", "lineHeight": 1.4
    },
