      "seed": 22, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "Travel Agent  (agent/travel_agent.py)\nLangGraph + LangChain\n\nsystem_prompt = skill.body\n  (or empty for no_skill)\n\nTools (9):\n  search_flights\n  search_hotels\n  create_booking\n  modify_booking\n  cancel_booking\n  get_fare_rules\n  check_availability\n  validate_passenger\n  get_itinerary\n\nModel: Gemini 2.5 Flash", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 2,
