      "seed": 26, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "Verifiers  (eval/verifiers/)\n\nToolCallVerifier\n  checks tool name + param keys\n  deterministic, zero API cost\n  score: 0.0–1.0\n  task.toml: verifier=\"tool_call_check\"\n\nLLMJudgeVerifier\n  Gemini 2.5 Flash via OpenRouter\n  criteria-aware (task.toml criteria=)\n  3 runs → averaged score\n  task.toml: verifier=\"llm_judge\"\n  use for quality/format tasks", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 13, "containerId": null, "originalText": "", "lineHeight": 1.4
