      "text": "Semantic Router  (eval/skill_router.py)\n\nModel: all-MiniLM-L6-v2  (80MB, local)\nEmbed skill descriptions once\nCosine sim on task instruction\nThreshold: 0.35  |  < 1ms / query\n\nUsed for: task-bank fallback matching\n           agent orchestration (Phase 8)", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 2,
