      "seed": 30, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "Gate Check  (eval/gate_check.py)\n\nweighted_delta = Σ(delta × weight) / Σw\nDomain weights: booking=3.0 flight/hotel=2.0\n\nT1 BLOCK    delta < -0.05  exit(1)\nT2 SOFT     delta < 0       exit(1)\nT3 WARN     small negative  exit(0)\nPASS        delta ≥ +0.05  exit(0)", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 13, "containerId": null, "originalText": "", "lineHeight": 1.4
