      "id": "t_langfuse", "type": "text", "x": 1915, "y": 720, "width": 770, "height": 280,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": null, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "boundElements": [],
      "seed": 34, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "Langfuse  (cloud.langfuse.com or self-hosted)\n\nFull LLM call tree per run\nTool call spans with latency\nverifier_score event pushed after run\nsession_id = task_id__run_id\n  → groups no_skill + with_skill runs\n\nTrace URL stored in EvalResult\n→ surfaced in PR comment for regressions\n\nKeys: LANGFUSE_PUBLIC_KEY / SECRET_KEY / HOST", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 13, "containerId": null, "originalText": "", "lineHeight": 1.4
    },
    {
      "id": "r_sqlite", "type": "rectangle", "x": 1900, "y": 1040, "width": 800, "height": 280,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#f43f5e", "backgroundColor": "#fff1f2", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": {"type": 3}, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "boundElements": [],
      "seed": 35, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "t_sqlite", "type": "text", "x": 1915, "y": 1050, "width": 770, "height": 260,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": null, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "boundElements": [],
      "seed": 36, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "SQLite Trajectory Store  (trajectory.db)\nLightweight local supplement to Langfuse\n\nruns table: task_id, condition, score, failure_mode\nsteps table: tool_name, latency_ms, tokens\n\n7 failure modes:\n  NO_TOOL_CALL  WRONG_TOOL  MISSING_PARAM\n  MULTI_STEP_DROPOUT  PARTIAL_MATCH\n  HALLUCINATED_ID  UNKNOWN\n\n→ feeds GRPO propose_skill clustering", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 13, "containerId": null, "originalText": "", "lineHeight": 1.4
    },
    {
      "id": "r_grpo", "type": "rectangle", "x": 50, "y": 1240, "width": 850, "height": 450,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#f59e0b", "backgroundColor": "#fef9c3", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": {"type": 3}, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "boundElements": [],
      "seed": 37, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "t_grpo", "type": "text", "x": 65, "y": 1252, "width": 820, "height": 430,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": null, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "boundElements": [],
      "seed": 38, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "GRPO Optimizer  (eval/optimizer/)\n\noptimizer.py — improve existing skill\n  K=5 variants × up to 5 rounds\n  generate_variant() via Gemini 2.5 Flash\n  fast-eval scores each variant\n  propose-only — NEVER auto-commits\n\npropose_skill.py — Phase 6.2\n  1. load_failure_clusters(trajectory.db)\n     OR load_clusters_from_ab_results()\n  2. skip domains with existing skill\n  3. cluster by domain + failure_mode (min 5)\n  4. draft_skill_body() via Gemini 2.5 Flash\n  5. open_skill_pr() via GitHub API\n     branch: proposal/<skill-name>\n     PR: \"proposal: auto-generated <skill>\"\n  6. CI eval gate runs on the PR\n  7. Human approves or closes — NEVER auto-merged", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 13, "containerId": null, "originalText": "", "lineHeight": 1.4
