    {
      "id": "t_path_a", "type": "text", "x": 2848, "y": 92, "width": 964, "height": 796,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": null, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "boundElements": [],
      "seed": 50, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "PATH A — skills generate\n(human-initiated, LLM-drafted)\n\n$ skills generate disruption-handling \\\n    --description \"Handle cancelled flights\n    and rebooking\" \\\n    --owner travel-platform\n\nFlow:\n1. validate name (VALID_SKILL_NAME regex)\n2. call Gemini 2.5 Flash via OpenRouter\n   GENERATE_PROMPT:\n     name + description →\n     structured SKILL.md body\n     (Workflow, Inputs, Output,\n      Edge Cases)\n3. build YAML frontmatter\n4. write skills/<name>/SKILL.md\n5. upsert registry.yaml (status: draft)\n\nOutput:\n\"Generated skill: skills/disruption-handling\nReview SKILL.md before opening a PR\"\n\nHuman reviews + edits\n→ opens PR\n→ CI eval gate runs\n→ PASS / BLOCK", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 13, "containerId": null, "originalText": "", "lineHeight": 1.4
    },
    {
      "id": "r_path_b", "type": "rectangle", "x": 2830, "y": 940, "width": 1000, "height": 830,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#fb923c", "backgroundColor": "#ffedd5", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": {"type": 3}, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "boundElements": [],
      "seed": 51, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "t_path_b", "type": "text", "x": 2848, "y": 952, "width": 964, "height": 806,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": null, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "boundElements": [],
      "seed": 52, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 1, "isDeleted": false, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "PATH B — GRPO auto-proposal\n(system-initiated, from failures)\n\n$ python -m eval.optimizer.propose_skill \\\n    --threshold 5 \\\n    --github-token ghp_... \\\n    --repo Tabhi-Commons/travel-agent-skills\n\nFlow:\n1. load_failure_clusters(trajectory.db)\n   OR load_clusters_from_ab_results()\n2. skip domains with existing skill\n3. group by domain + failure_mode\n   require >= threshold (default 5)\n4. draft_skill_body() \n   Gemini 2.5 Flash:\n   failure context → SKILL.md body\n5. open_skill_pr() via GitHub API\n   branch: proposal/<skill-name>\n   commit: skills/<name>/SKILL.md\n   PR title: \"proposal: auto-generated <name>\"\n6. CI eval gate runs automatically on PR\n7. Human reviews content\n   approves or closes\n   NEVER auto-merged\n\n--dry-run flag: print proposals, no PR", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "baseline": 13, "containerId": null, "originalText": "", "lineHeight": 1.4
    },
